co-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eux1665703132929.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eux1665703132929.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eux1665703132929.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eux1665703132929\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"eux1665703132929__ureadstringsyssetting_408709\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Read a string from the specified section of a specified <span class=\"ph filepath\">ini</span>\n      file.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"eux1665703132929__topic_d123884e1_d123885e1_d123886e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104eux1665703132929_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"eux1665703132929__codeblock_dqt_23k_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">int ureadstringsyssetting (char*section, char*key,\n\n    char*default, char*value, intmax, char*iniFile);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eux1665703132929__topic_d87507e1_d87508e1_d87509e1_d87510e1_d87511e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d629315e64\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"eux1665703132929__parml_zs4_g3k_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">section</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the section containing the specified key</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">key</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the key whose associated string is to be retrieved.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">default</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Default value to be copied to <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var> if <var class=\"keyword varname\">key</var>\n                  is not found in the initialization file. This parameter cannot be NULL.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Requested value (Output)</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">max</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Size of the buffer pointed to by <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var>.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">iniFile</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the initialization file. If this name is not fully qualified, Uniface\n                  uses the standard Windows search path for initialization files.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eux1665703132929__topic_d87512e1_d87513e1_d87514e1_d87515e1_d87516e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d629315e143\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eux1665703132929__p_d123917e1_d123918e1_d123919e1\">The length of the string that was copied into <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var>, not including the zero terminator. This function never returns an error.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eux1665703132929__topic_d87517e1_d87518e1_d87519e1_d87520e1_d87521e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d629315e155\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eux1665703132929__d6584e20\">Microsoft Windows platforms only. Library:\n          <span class=\"ph filepath\">ulib</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eux1665703132929__topic_d87522e1_d87523e1_d87524e1_d87525e1_d87526e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d629315e168\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eux1665703132929__p_d123929e1_d123930e1_d123931e1\">This function is a wrapper for the Windows API\n            function <code class=\"ph codeph\">GetPrivateProfileString</code> and follows the same rules. For\n            extensive information about this function, visit the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"http://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/docs/\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Microsoft DN technical documentation</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104eux1665703132929_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"eux1665703132929__codeblock_sg3_x3k_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nchar val[200];\nureadstringsyssetting(\"mysection\", \"mykey\",\n\"foobar\", val, sizeof(val)-1, ugetprofile());</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zft1665703132860.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ugetprofile</a><p>Return a pointer to the name of the current .ini file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsu1665703133058.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uwritestringsyssetting</a><p>Copies a string to a specified section of a specified ini file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527332\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527332\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ureadstringsyssetting Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Read a string from the specified section of a specified ini file. Explain this code int ureadstringsyssetting (char*section, char*key, char*default, char*value, intmax, char*iniFile); Copy Parameters section Name of the section containing the specified key key Name of the key whose associated string is to be retrieved. default Default value to be copied to value if key is not found in the initialization file. This parameter cannot be NULL. value Requested value (Output) max Size of the buffer pointed to by value . iniFile Name of the initialization file. If this name is not fully qualified, Uniface uses the standard Windows search path for initialization files. Return Values The length of the string that was copied into value , not including the zero terminator. This function never returns an error. Use Microsoft Windows platforms only. Library: ulib Description This function is a wrapper for the Windows API function GetPrivateProfileString and follows the same rules. For extensive information about this function, visit the Microsoft DN technical documentation . Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> char val[200]; ureadstringsyssetting(\"mysection\", \"mykey\", \"foobar\", val, sizeof(val)-1, ugetprofile()); Copy Related Links ugetprofile Return a pointer to the name of the current .ini file. uwritestringsyssetting Copies a string to a specified section of a specified ini file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}